      "title": "South Korea's biggest arms buyer revealed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "South Korea is set to supply Poland with nearly 1,000 tanks, more than 600 artillery pieces and nearly 50 fighter jets, marking the biggest arms deal ever in Seoul.",
        "The multi-billion dollar deal is considered the largest and most significant Polish security order in recent years.",
        "It will significantly strengthen the country's armed forces, Poland's Ministry of Defense announced in a press release."
      ],
